<div>
    <h1>1.) What types of data we collect</h1>
</div>

<p>
    * The information you give to us.<br />
    This includes Email, password, phone number. We do not send any personal infomation
    other users and make sure this information is super secure.<br />
    * The information about your device.<br />
    When we collect your device we collect, the model number, serial number, the device settings, device settings,
    operating system IP address and other unique identifiers.<br />
