    games and applications that are not published by FlareCo.<br />
    * Parents or guardians may review, modify, or delete the child’s personal information, or 
    withdraw consent, by contacting us using the contact information provided at the end of this privacy policy, and may manage which 
    third-party games and applications can access and use the child’s Mythical Canine's Account information through parental controls.<br />
</p>

